Nissan

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Nissan Motor Company)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the multinational automobile manufacturer. For other uses, see Nissan (disambiguation).
Coordinates: 35°27′39″N 139°37′45″E﻿ / ﻿35.460883°N 139.6291854°E﻿ / 35.460883; 139.6291854

Nissan Motor Co., Ltd.









Nissan global headquarters in Yokohama, Japan




Native name

日産自動車株式会社



Romanized name

Nissan Jidōsha Kabushiki-gaisha



Type

Public (K.K.)


Traded as



TYO: 7201
